'''Enchū Suwa/Kosaka Enchū''' (諏訪 円忠/小坂 円忠) ([[:en:Einin|Einin]] 3 ([[:en:1295|1295]]) – [[:en:Jōji|Jōji]] 3 ([[:en:1364|1364]])) was an official of the [[:en:Kamakura shogunate|Kamakura shogunate]] and {{ill|Muromachi shogunate|ja|Ashikaga Shogunate|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Muromachi shogunate|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, and the founder of the {{ill|Suwa clan|ja|諏訪氏#京都諏訪氏|Suwa clan=Suwa clan|lt=Kyoto Suwa clan|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suwa clan|qq=}}. He is the author of the [[:en:Suwa Daimyōjin Ekotoba|Suwa Daimyōjin Ekotoba]].
